If anyone wants to look at our Kaggle, it is here: https://t.co/w5Zx8gLrWD. If you have any questions, please ask. Thank you once again to the NFL for hosting this competition each year, especially to @StatsbyLopez and @DataWithBliss , among others. 

#BigDataBowl #nflverse

Here's formations for KC vs Seattle. 11p or 12p for 85% of the snaps. Watson in for all 5 of the 13p snaps, where there's only 1 WR on the field. That's a heavy personnel, and 4 runs out of 5 snaps. Our least effective formation, too. 

#nflverse #rstats https://t.co/a17IvaUCjP

Here's our defense. Pretty stifling overall. Not sure what's happening with Karlaftis's snaps, honestly. I guess just keeping him fresh for the stretch run. All of Cooks snaps came with 6 DB's on the field.
